strings: <voice_0x01000D0A><se_low>King Trode: Well Yangus, at least you were right about something! No one here so much as bats an eyelid at me!

<voice_0x01000D0B><se_low>King Trode: So...the pub awaits! I'll go on ahead.
I wouldn't want to get in your way.

<voice_0x01000D0C><se_low>King Trode: You go and find this Brains fellow.
I'll be waiting for your report!

<voice_0x01000D0D><se_low>Yangus: Waitin'? Boozin' more like! Come on, guv!
Let's forget about 'im an' 'ead over to Brains's.
<voice_0x01000D0E><se_low>Yangus: Some of us 'ave gotta keep our minds on the job, eh? We gotta find that Dhoulmagus.
